程序包 Model

类 User

java.lang.Object
Model.User
public class User extends Object
Represents a user in the Smart Finance Application. This class encapsulates user account details, including personal information, account status, balance, and a list of associated transactions. It provides methods for CSV serialization, deserialization, and transaction management.
版本:
1.0
作者:
Group 19
